<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2026-07-03T22:21:57-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, 20 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">5th St. Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260703/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="5th St. Sunset" /><published>2026-07-03T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-07-03T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/fifth</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260703/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Setting sun reflects in the water at 5th St. in Hermosa Beach.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">5thストリートのサンセット</span>
ハーモサビーチ、5thストリートの水面に映る夕日。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Clouds" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Setting sun reflects in the water at 5th St. in Hermosa Beach. 5thストリートのサンセット ハーモサビーチ、5thストリートの水面に映る夕日。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0463-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0463-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Foot of Longfellow</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260702/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Foot of Longfellow" /><published>2026-07-02T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-07-02T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/longfellow</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260702/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Postcard photo of footprints on the sand at sunset. On the beach at Longfellow St.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ロングフェローの足元
</span>
夕暮れ時の砂浜に刻まれた足跡を写した絵葉書。ロングフェロー通りが浜辺に突き当たる場所にて。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Postcard photo of footprints on the sand at sunset. On the beach at Longfellow St. ロングフェローの足元 夕暮れ時の砂浜に刻まれた足跡を写した絵葉書。ロングフェロー通りが浜辺に突き当たる場所にて。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0327-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2607_DSCF0327-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sandy Beach</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260629/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sandy Beach" /><published>2026-06-29T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-29T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kelp</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260629/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Kelp washed up on the shore creates a nice composition amid small waves at Rat Beach in Torrance.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">砂浜</span>
トーランスのラット・ビーチ(通称) では、岸に打ち上げられた昆布が、小波の中で美しい構図を作り出している。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Kelp washed up on the shore creates a nice composition amid small waves at Rat Beach in Torrance. 砂浜 トーランスのラット・ビーチ(通称) では、岸に打ち上げられた昆布が、小波の中で美しい構図を作り出している。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_DSCF0070.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_DSCF0070.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Rat Beach</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260628/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Rat Beach" /><published>2026-06-28T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-28T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/rat-beach</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260628/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Birds watching the setting sun at Torrance's Rat Beach. The late afternoon sun gives the kelp a bright orange glow.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ラット・ビーチ</span>
トーランスのラット・ビーチで、夕日を眺める鳥たち。午後遅くの陽射しが、昆布を鮮やかなオレンジ色に染めている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Birds watching the setting sun at Torrance's Rat Beach. The late afternoon sun gives the kelp a bright orange glow. ラット・ビーチ トーランスのラット・ビーチで、夕日を眺める鳥たち。午後遅くの陽射しが、昆布を鮮やかなオレンジ色に染めている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_DSCF0105-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_DSCF0105-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sidewalk</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260626/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sidewalk" /><published>2026-06-26T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-26T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sidewalk</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260626/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A tree-lined sidewalk on a four lane street.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">歩道</span>
4車線の道路沿いに木々が立ち並ぶ歩道だ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Street" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A tree-lined sidewalk on a four lane street. 歩道 4車線の道路沿いに木々が立ち並ぶ歩道だ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_IMG_2711.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_IMG_2711.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Redondo View</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260625/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Redondo View" /><published>2026-06-25T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-25T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/redondo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260625/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Looking at South Redondo Beach from Palos Verdes. The large silver building in the distance is Sofi Stadium, one of the venues where the FIFA World Cup soccer tournament is taking place.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">レドンド・ビュー</span>
パロス・ベルデスからサウス・レドンド・ビーチを眺めた光景だ。遠くに見える大きな銀色の建物は、FIFAワールドカップの開催会場の一つである SoFiスタジアムだ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking at South Redondo Beach from Palos Verdes. The large silver building in the distance is Sofi Stadium, one of the venues where the FIFA World Cup soccer tournament is taking place. レドンド・ビュー パロス・ベルデスからサウス・レドンド・ビーチを眺めた光景だ。遠くに見える大きな銀色の建物は、FIFAワールドカップの開催会場の一つである SoFiスタジアムだ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02563_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02563_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">8th Street</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260624/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="8th Street" /><published>2026-06-24T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-24T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/8th-st</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260624/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A walkstreet in Hermosa Beach, the last block before the sand. So pleasant without cars.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp"></span>
ハーモサビーチにあるウォークストリート。砂浜の手前、最後のブロックだ。車がいないと、ずいぶん気持ちがいい。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Street" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A walkstreet in Hermosa Beach, the last block before the sand. So pleasant without cars. ハーモサビーチにあるウォークストリート。砂浜の手前、最後のブロックだ。車がいないと、ずいぶん気持ちがいい。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02547_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02547_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Mountain in the Sand</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260616/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Mountain in the Sand" /><published>2026-06-16T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-16T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sand-mountain</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260616/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Marks on the sand at low tide, like a sumi-e ink painting.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">砂の中の山</span>
干潮時の砂に刻まれた跡は、まるで墨絵のようだ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Dawn" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Marks on the sand at low tide, like a sumi-e ink painting. 砂の中の山 干潮時の砂に刻まれた跡は、まるで墨絵のようだ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02348_edit-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02348_edit-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">SoCal Suburbia</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260615/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="SoCal Suburbia" /><published>2026-06-15T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-15T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/suburbia</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260615/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The colorful uniformity of a Southern California planned community. Blue skies and the soft light of the fog rolling in.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">南カリフォルニアの郊外</span>
南カリフォルニアの計画都市が醸し出す、色彩豊かな均一感。青い空と、流れ込む霧の柔らかな光。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The colorful uniformity of a Southern California planned community. Blue skies and the soft light of the fog rolling in. 南カリフォルニアの郊外 南カリフォルニアの計画都市が醸し出す、色彩豊かな均一感。青い空と、流れ込む霧の柔らかな光。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02308_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02308_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">King Harbor</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260614/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="King Harbor" /><published>2026-06-14T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-14T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/king-harbor</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260614/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The setting sun reflects in the water, at the entrance to King Harbor in Redondo Beach.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">キング・ハーバー</span>
レドンド・ビーチのキング・ハーバーの入り口で、夕日が水面に映る。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Harbors" /><category term="King Harbor" /><category term="Piers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The setting sun reflects in the water, at the entrance to King Harbor in Redondo Beach. キング・ハーバー レドンド・ビーチのキング・ハーバーの入り口で、夕日が水面に映る。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02280-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02280-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>